xml

Class DatasetInformation

  • java.lang.Object
    • xml.DatasetInformation

  • public class DatasetInformation
extends java.lang.Object
    This class defines the information that is saved in the XML file associated to each intermediate or pre-processed dataset file created.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      static class  DatasetInformation.AttributeStatistics
      This class defines a set of statistical metrics of an attribute of a intermediate dataset or pre-processed dataset file.
      static class  DatasetInformation.Statistic
      This class defines the information collected for a statistical metric of each attribute of a intermediate dataset or pre-processed dataset file.
